					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">Composite video looks quite shitty no matter how you capture it, so I think it's a waste to get expensive capture devices. The important thing is to make sure that no frames/fields are being dropped during the capture, so you can post-process the video and make it look more authentic.</div>

